{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ri0 \i0 \qj \fs20 \li0 
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \ul0 \strike0 \i0 \fs20 \sa0 \sb0 
In a sequel to Rumsfeld v. Forum for Academic and Institutional Rights, Inc.,
}
{\b0 \cf19 \f2 \i0 \fs16 
{\*\bkmkstart co_fnRef_Idb76d143279a11f1bc1683b4c14c7e}{\*\bkmkend co_fnRef_Idb76d143279a11f1bc1683b4c14c7e}
